{
  "texts": [
    "Context-awareness empowers IoT systems to sieve and prioritize data predicated on its pertinence to specific contexts, mitigating information deluge and enhancing decision-making.",
    "CA systems further enable IoT devices to exhibit greater proactivity in addressing user requisites.",
    "By discerning the user's context and preferences, IoT devices can preempt needs and operate autonomously, obviating the necessity for explicit user directives and crafting a more fluid and intuitive user experience.",
    "Integrating Context Into IoT Frameworks Role of Context-AwarenessContext-awareness is a pivotal aspect of IoT applications that enhances their effectiveness and relevance in various domains.",
    "Understanding the importance of context-awareness is vital for harnessing the full potential of IoT in delivering personalized and intelligent services."
  ]
}